snippet.title: NSMB2 Mushroom Madness - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Mushroom Madness is an NSMB2 Mod made mostly by myself, with a bit of help from others in some places. The mod will feature 12 brand new levels across 2 worlds all based around mushrooms. 

Update : The mod is out now! Here's the release trailer with the download link in the description: https://youtu.be/ez-1KKun-qg

Leveldesign / Trailer Editing: 
Mushroom

Gameplay Recording:
Tablu: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCREZ06jPygenrSXJhB8fUpg
